=== Base of Operations === The Ankoku-no-Miyatsuko governed from [[:en:Yasu District, Shiga|Yasu District]] in Ōmi Province, corresponding to modern [[:en:Yasu, Shiga|Yasu]] and [[:en:Moriyama, Shiga|Moriyama]] in [[:en:Shiga Prefecture|Shiga Prefecture]]. Some sources suggest they later came under the control of the {{ill|Ōmi-no-Kuni no Miyatsuko|ja|淡海国造|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōmi-no-Kuni no Miyatsuko|qq=}} [citation needed].
